title: Future Bass 2014 Ministry Of Sound (2014) (AciDToX8)
description:
Future Bass 2014 Ministry Of Sound (2014) 

        Bass, Tech, Club, Funky, House | Ministry of Sound Recordings

          VBR kbps | MP3 | mixed + split | 2014 | 02:05:11 | 483 Mb


Featuring deep house from pioneering acts such as Disclosure, Storm Queen, Breach, Rudimental, Le Youth, Tensnake, XXXY and Toyboy & Robin along with a true melange of liquid drum and bass, post dubstep and garage inspired house from Shadow Child, Alix Perez, Bobby Tank, Breakage, Cyantific and Maya Jane Coles. Future Bass 2014 is a true reflection of UK dance music as it currently stands and features a collection of tracks from the artists that are consistently pushing new sounds forward.
